VITE_USDC_ADDRESS=0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000001
VITE_USDT_ADDRESS=0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000001



 Set Environment Variables: Configure .env with:
   - (from Privy dashboard)
   - VITE_ESCROW_CONTRACT_ADDRESS (deployed contract)
   - VITE_USDC_ADDRESS / VITE_USDT_ADDRESS (testnet tokens)
   - VITE_RPC_URL (Polkadot Hub RPC)
